name: ClippingPathType
shortdesc: The type of clipping path to create.

property.name: DETECT_EDGES
property.shortdesc: The clipping path is based on pixel value threshold and tolerance.

property.name: ALPHA_CHANNEL
property.shortdesc: The clipping path is based on an alpha channel defined for the graphic in a graphics application.

property.name: PHOTOSHOP_PATH
property.shortdesc: The clipping path is defined for the graphic in Photoshop.

property.name: USER_MODIFIED_PATH
property.shortdesc: (Read-only) The clipping path has been manually edited.
